OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Families get
OL,4,C'confirmation public inquiry will take
OL,5,Cplace'
OL,7,FA public inquiry is to be held to
OL,8,Fexamine the events which led to Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane stabbing three people to
OL,10,Fdeath in Nottingham in June last year.
OL,12,FA review into the treatment given to
OL,13,FValdo Calocane who went on to stab and
OL,14,Fkill three people, found there were a
OL,15,Fseries of errors, omissions, and
OL,16,Fmisjudgements in his care:
OL,18,FHe was ordered to be detained earlier
OL,19,Fthis year after admitting manslaughter
OL,20,Fon the grounds of diminished
OL,21,Fresponsibility.
