OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Families get
OL,4,C'confirmation public inquiry will take
OL,5,Cplace'
OL,7,FCalocane stabbed 19-year-old students
OL,8,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,9,FKumar as they returned from a night
OL,10,Fout in the early hours of June 13th
OL,11,Flast year, before killing 65-year-old
OL,12,FIan Coates.
OL,14,FA statement from their families
OL,15,Frevealed they have had confirmation
OL,16,Fthat a public inquiry will take place,
OL,17,Fafter meeting Health Secretary Wes
OL,18,FStreeting and Attorney General Richard
OL,19,FHermer.
