OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Families get
OL,4,C'confirmation public inquiry will take
OL,5,Cplace'
OL,7,FIt said: "Following meetings with the
OL,8,FAttorney General and Health Secretary
OL,9,Fon Tuesday of last week, we are
OL,10,Fpleased to have had confirmation that
OL,11,Fa public inquiry will take place.
OL,13,F"The final form of the inquiry is yet
OL,14,Fto be determined, but we families urge
OL,15,Fthat it must be a statutory, judge-led
OL,16,Fone."
