OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Families get
OL,4,C'confirmation public inquiry will take
OL,5,Cplace'
OL,7,FIt comes after the final part of a
OL,8,Fspecial Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,9,Freview into the care of Calocane by
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust (NHFT), found risk
OL,12,Fassessments "minimised or omitted" key
OL,13,Fdetails of the serious risk he posed
OL,14,Fto others.
OL,16,FIt also questioned how well the trust
OL,17,Fengaged with Calocane's family, who
OL,18,Fraised concerns about his mental state.
OL,20,FThe families' statement added:
OL,26,@tD@MOUtD@bO]
