OL,7,F"Progress is slowly being made and we
OL,8,Fwill continue in our fight to ensure
OL,9,Fthere is full organisational and
OL,10,Findividual accountability for the
OL,11,Fhorrific events of 13 June 2023.
OL,13,F"We will also fight to ensure that
OL,14,Fappropriate changes and improvements
OL,15,Fto our systems and laws are made so as
OL,16,Fto ensure that a tragedy of this level
OL,17,Fis prevented from ever happening
OL,18,Fagain."
