OL,7,FIt also emerged that a psychiatrist
OL,8,Fwarned Calocane could "end up killing
OL,9,Fsomeone" three years before the
OL,10,Fattacks in June 2023.
OL,12,FHis family told Panorama they only
OL,13,Freceived the 300-page medical summary
OL,14,Fcontaining the warning after his
OL,15,Fsentencing.
OL,17,FCalocane was handed an indefinite
OL,18,Fhospital order in January, after
OL,19,Fadmitting manslaughter on the grounds
OL,20,Fof diminished responsibility.
