OL,7,FProsecutors accepted his not-guilty
OL,8,Fpleas to murder after multiple medical
OL,9,Fexperts concluded he had paranoid
OL,10,Fschizophrenia.
OL,12,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,13,FCare and the Attorney General have
OL,14,Fbeen approached for comment.
